  <figure class="container-prose post-hero">
    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-5-2025-10_02_34-PM.png" alt="FHA Loan Qualifications: Your Complete Guide to Qualifying with Minimal Down Payment" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
